<td width="179">
<p style="margin-top: 4px;"><img src="http://www.tonyblake.com/TESTsites/honeywell_email/images/Round_Team.jpg" alt="" width="160" height="160" /></p>
</td>
<td width="471">
<p style="color: #c90431; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; margin-top: 6px; margin-bottom: 6px;">Now, what can we do for you?</p>
<p style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 4px;">The Honeywell Customer Experience Team is here to do everything we can to make your job easier, our customers happier, and our company more responsive and successful.</p>
<p style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 4px;">To do that, we need to hear from you. What are your points of frustration when you&rsquo;re working with a customer? Or, just as importantly, what&rsquo;s working for you that might benefit others in your same situation?</p>
<p style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 4px;">We&rsquo;ll work to find answers to your questions, and share your suggestions. Watch your email for more.</p>
<p style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 4px;">The Honeywell Customer Experience Team is on your team.</p>
</td>
